<h1>Memorandum</h1>

<div class="docbody">
<div class="opener">
<table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">[Mount Vernon, 175859]</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
</div>
<p style="text-indent: 0;">A List of Lands given unto the Clerk of Fairfax Countyin the year 1758 to be Taxed.</p>
<table class="bodytext" id="Col06d136t1">
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;">Acres</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap;">In Frederick County.<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0149-fn-0001" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0149-fn-0001-ptr">1</a></td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;">viz.one Tract of</td>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;">760</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;">one Ditto of</td>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;">552</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;">one Ditto of</td>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;">550</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;">one Ditto of</td>
	      <td class="num" style="border-bottom: 1px solid black; padding-right: 0.5em !important;">453</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;">2315</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap;">In Fairfax County.</td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;">viz.Mount Vernon Tract</td>
	      <td class="num" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;">1900</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td style="white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;">bought of S. Darrell</td>
	      <td class="num" style="border-bottom: 1px solid black; padding-right: 0.5em !important;">500</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td class="num" style="border-bottom: 1px solid black; padding-right: 0.5em !important;">2400</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td></td>
	      <td></td>
	      <td class="num" style="border-bottom: 1px solid black; padding-right: 0.5em !important;">4715</td>
	    </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin-top: 1em; text-indent: 0;">N.B. I gave in the same List for the year 1759 &amp; paid Taxes for both years to Colo. John West<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0149-fn-0002" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0149-fn-0002-ptr">2</a> as will appear by his Receipt No. 1 Viz.</p>

<table class="bodytext" id="Col06d136t2">
<tr>
	      <td class="par" colspan="4">Taxes For the year 1758 on 4715 Acres @ 2s.3d. prCt<a class="ptr" href="#GEWN-02-06-02-0149-fn-0003" id="GEWN-02-06-02-0149-fn-0003-ptr">3</a> comes to</td>
	      <td class="curr" style="padding-right: 0.5em !important;">10.6.1</td>
	    </tr>
<tr>
	      <td></td>
